menssage started....

Subject: The ants go marching on...hoora....hoora


    Hell Beast looked to the scanners and to the probe dancing around 
outside. It was curious, and probly a trap. He locked on to its 
signiture, 
"Probe, what do you want with me?!"

    Megatron marvled at his success. Five clones of Inferno lied next 
to the 
original. Unfortunetly, the pigment of the armor went a little bad 
and the 
clones turned blue. That was no matter, though, he was going to 
dispatch them 
to crush Phobia, Kitkat, and all of there disgusting little soldiers.
    "Inferno! Clones! Get up. You have a mission." Megatron barked as 
they 
got up and marched over in a neat colum over to Megatron.
    "Our Queen, what are your orders?" Inferno said, the official 
general of 
the clones. He was red, while the others were blue.
    Megatron gave him a map, "Find Phobia, and destroy him and any of 
his 
allies. I want them destroyed, do you understand?"
    Inferno, and the clones, saluted. "There will be nothing left of 
them! 
Troops, take to the air!"
    The CLones, and Inferno, went into flight mode and exited the 
cave headed 
into the darkness of the artic night, looking for Phobia, or waitng 
for 
Phobia to find them.
